@startuml
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam diagramBorderColor transparent
skinparam diagramBorderThickness 0

skinparam participant {
  BorderColor #333333
  BackgroundColor #eeeeee
  FontSize 13
  FontColor #333333
  Padding 8
}

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #555555
  ArrowThickness 1.5
  LifeLineBorderColor #bbbbbb
  ArrowFontSize 11
  ArrowFontColor #444444
}

participant "주문" as O
participant "오케스트레이터" as Orch
participant "상품" as P
participant "배달" as D

O -> Orch: ① 주문 생성됨
Orch -> P: ② 재고 차감
P --> Orch: ③ 차감 완료
Orch -> D: ④ 배달 생성
D --> Orch: ⑤ 생성 완료
Orch -> O: ⑥ 주문 완료

@enduml
